{
  "stem": "24346.6",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In fact, I mentioned before, that first they sent papers, my brother left two or four weeks before me, and he already had a job working in the union as a butcher.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I asked him, Avrum, how do you do-- He said where the union is.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So I said to them, thank you so much.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I appreciate what you want to do, but I can't accept it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't want no charity.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "This is a free country.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I see, you can get a job.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Everything's available only if you want to work.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I want to work.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I got to find a job for myself.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So they say, we have no choice if you don't want it, we can't help it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "In the meantime, this aunt went for a vacation, another aunt took us in.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "With this first aunt, we were two weeks, the other aunt, we're maybe a month or six weeks.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But since I decided I wanted a job, I went-- me as a greenhorn, just came off the boat-- from Paterson, New Jersey, traveled by bus and by train, subway, to Union Square, walked over to the union-- couldn't speak English, a few words, here and there.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I went by train.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I found everything.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Went to the union.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I told them, I don't know how they make baloney, here, but I'm a baloney maker from Europe.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It may not be right for you, but I want a job as a baloney maker.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He said, where do you live?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I said in Paterson, New Jersey.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He said, you have to travel 2 hours to the job, work 8 to 10 hours and travel 2-- no, sorry.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We can't give you a job.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
